Step 1:
- vim /etc/apt/sources.list
	Add:
	deb http://nginx.org/packages/debian/ squeeze nginx
	deb-src http://nginx.org/packages/debian/ squeeze nginx

Step 2:
apt-get install nginx

Step 3:
cp /projects/subman/ssl/* /usr/local/nginx/ssl/
cp /projects/subman/conf/nginx_subman.conf /etc/nginx/site-enabled/


* Should the certificates not work, generate new ones by following these instructions: http://www.akadia.com/services/ssh_test_certificate.html

